title: Lil Mo and Dynamite Interview and More
itunes:title: Lil Mo and Dynamite Interview and More
description:
1/23/19 - Today on the show we had Lil Mo and her husband, boxer Dynamite stop by, and lets just say they did not hold their tongue. They spoke on being on "Marriage Boot Camp", Lil Mo controversy comments towards Queen Naija, R. Kelly and more. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a Colorado man who  threatened to kill women because he’s a virgin and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
